snippet.title: WavesArt
snippet.description:
WavesArt is an advanced sound developing company targeting the best Workstations & Arrangers that are capable of applying premium Acoustic instruments & Orchestras emulation very close to VST industrial sound libraries.
Antony Sharmman is the coordinator sound engineer that has performed libraries demos in real time.
Official Website : https://wavesart.eu
www.facebook.com/WavesArts
